==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Coalescence
<hw>Co`a*les"cence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or
state of growing together, as similar parts; the act of uniting by
natural affinity or attraction; the state of being united; union;
concretion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coalescent</ent>⟦br⟧
